metadata.name: it's time #1
metadata.description:
‘It’s time’ is the commemorative token for the seed round of phase I that celebrates mfers going onchain. The artwork by Thompson represents a tradable placeholder token for the 112 mfer base layers.  If you are holding the art at the time of the layer token airdrop, you will receive a randomized, onchain & tradable base layer token. This will complete phase I of the coveted onchain mfer base layers…
Learn more at http://onchainmfers.xyz
